text: Sin Sophanat (born 20 April 1997) is a Cambodian footballer who plays for Visakha in the Cambodian League. ==Club career== Sin Sophanat made his senior debut in Cambodia League on 16 March 2019 Vs Soltilo Angkor. ==International career== Sin Sophanat made his debut in 2020 AFC U-23 Championship qualification against Australia national under-23 soccer team on 22 March 2019. == External links == *Sin Sophanat at NationalFootballTeams Category:Living people Category:1997 births Category:Cambodian footballers Category:Cambodia international footballers Category:Association football defenders Category:Sportspeople from Phnom Penh Category:Competitors at the 2019 Southeast Asian Games
